🌍 Exclusive Weekend in Langhe, UNESCO World Heritage Site.
🍇 Hilly stretched as far as the eye can see, on which ancient villages and castles are perched, a succession of gentle slopes planted with vines the rows of which make beautiful geometric shapes.
- 2 SPIRGRIPS+ Limited Edition: a unique product in magnesium made in CNC;
- 2 guests;
- 2 nights in a typical resort in Langhe (5 stars hotel);
- breakfast, lunch, and dinner included;
- tasting of local IGP foods in Barolo (truffles, cheese, hazelnuts, and more)
- special bike tour with Pascal Badolet;
- tour around the most typical towns with a local guide;
- transfer from the airport;
- flight not included;
For more info write us!

